    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 6th level, you add the @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.oyE5nVppa5mde5gT]{Animate Dead} spell to your spellbook if it is not there already. When you cast @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.oyE5nVppa5mde5gT]{Animate Dead}, you can animate two corpses instead of one.</p>\n<p>Whenever you create an undead using a necromancy spell, it has additional benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The creature's hit point maximum is increased by an amount equal to your wizard level.</li>\n<li>The creature adds your proficiency bonus to its weapon damage rolls.</li>\n</ul>",
